{"tid":2054941,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"口交部：暫停77國家地區債務償還","createTime":"2020-06-07T14:11:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-07T14:27:50.000Z","uid":48083,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"6b0297d9c4bb2f8a5319b42cb8c4b81b69db4dcc","tid":2054941,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T14:11:28.000Z","msg":"國務院新聞辦7日上午舉行新聞發布會，介紹《抗擊新冠肺炎疫情的中國行動》白皮書有關情況並答記者問。外交部副部長馬朝旭表示，中國已經宣布向77個發展中國家和地區暫停債務償還。<br />\n<br />\n馬朝旭稱，⋯⋯中國一向是言必信、行必果，說到的一定做到⋯⋯<br />\n⋯⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n關於聯合國人道主義應急倉庫和樞紐在中國的建設，正在商談和加緊籌建之中。中國還積極參與並落實20國集團暫緩最貧困國家債務償付的倡議，已經宣布向77個發展中國家和地區暫停債務償還。30個中非對口醫院合作機制也正在加緊建立。（編輯：梁翠婷）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.exmoo.com/article/150488.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.exmoo.com%2Farticle%2F150488.html&d=gQ7zj4J1baFceLD6a1UzUuaWbb7ReRbDtXxzMsl%2FlTw%3D&h=3f4a1a89\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.exmoo.com/article/150488.html</a>"},{"pid":"7ba3ce3e3c1ea938372e5e95a15bf40d72dc28fb","tid":2054941,"uid":241504,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T14:12:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/x9C96UM.png\" /><br />\n<blockquote>俾仇B對鞋踢春袋一定好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我想試吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/avkEknV\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/avkEknV</a>"},{"pid":"54f40a10fd165dcf8548019feec27a920eabc2d9","tid":2054941,"uid":2054,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T14:13:57.000Z","msg":"搞地攤經濟去養班非洲豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/as